Kubernets will host a docker container with full autoscaling, logs, security & others....


borg is used in google & kubernets came from there...

refer this link for some container tools --> www.cncf.io

install this 


install kubectl
install virtualbox
https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
Change the exe name to virtualbox

install minikube
https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/tools/install-minikube/

Change the exe name to minikube
minikube start

or 

minikube start --disk 1g --cpus 2 --memory 2048

this will create a Virtual server in your laptop...
